      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, offering a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a unit of peerless mechanical and aesthetic integrity. Every detail reflects meticulous stewardship, ensuring an experience indistinguishable from new.",
